    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/0fa1a2865f81cb2b617bc45e4cecef5e.avif?t=1770961032\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「集结30名同伴前来魔王城吧！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，国王收到了人类的宿敌——魔王寄来的信。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然很明显是个陷阱，但国王决定利用这个机会，趁势达到压制魔王城的目的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被选中的指挥官，即是新人卢瑟夫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卢瑟夫接受了国王的委托，踏上寻找性格各异的30名同伴，攻略魔王城的旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/c32a70189f770af5706649d227833256.avif?t=1770961032\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内容分两部，总计60名角色登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804020/extras/08a02d33b7fb0d54aae9f50fe1709fd3.avif?t=1770961032\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日式战棋类游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登场角色达60人，增添战斗组合乐趣</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >据点设置时间概念，某些角色只在特定时间特定场所出现。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的剧情任务</p></li></ul>",
